      "line": 30,
      "message": "In the original design for logging (which you can still see in some components), the filebeat configuration file was stored as a file under resources/config/logging and injected into a configMap.  It wasn't overridable via values (except for two data elements that were placed in values.yaml).\nI put it here to avoid repeating it in every single component that uses it.",
